STATE EX REL. WBNS 10-TV, INC.
v.
HAWKINS 2019-0189 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 7, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

In Mandamus and Prohibition. Sua sponte, respondent ordered to file a response, if any, to relator's complaint and motion for peremptory writ no later than 12:00 p.m. on Tuesday, February 12, 2019.
